<% future_post = site.resources.get("articles/future-post") %>

<p>To see a demo for the future post showing, you'll need to:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Open the file at  <code><%= future_post.asset.path %></code></li>
  <li>Change the date from <code><%= future_post.data.fetch("publish_at") %></code> to something in the near future, like 10 minutes from now: <code><%= 10.minutes.from_now.to_formatted_s(:long) %></code></li>
  <li>Save the file, then wait for the publish date and time to pass, refresh the site, and you'll see the post.</li>
</ol>
